ZH: 我已经养成了每天早晨喝一杯咖啡的习惯。
EN: I have developed a habit of drinking a cup of coffee every morning.

ZH: 她习惯了晚上独自散步。
EN: She is accustomed to taking a walk alone at night.

ZH: 我们应该养成良好的学习习惯。
EN: We should cultivate good study habits.

ZH: 孩子们在学校里培养了团队合作的习惯。
EN: The children have formed a habit of teamwork at school.

ZH: 我不喜欢吃辣的食物,所以不会养成吃火锅的习惯。
EN: I don't like spicy food, so I won't develop a habit of eating hot pot.

ZH: 动物在寒冷的季节会蜷缩起来以保持身体温暖的习惯。
EN: Animals have a habit of curling up to keep warm in cold seasons.

ZH: 我们总是在周末去散步,形成了一个健康的习惯。
EN: We always go for a walk on weekends, forming a healthy habit.

ZH: 他养成了每天锻炼的好习惯。
EN: He has developed a good habit of exercising every day.

ZH: 在外国旅行时,养成尊重当地风俗的习惯是很重要的。
EN: It is important to cultivate a habit of respecting local customs when traveling abroad.

ZH: 晚上看手机对眼睛不好,不要养成这个习惯。
EN: It is not good for your eyes to look at your phone at night, do not develop this habit.

ZH: 她习惯把钥匙挂在门口。
EN: She is used to hanging the keys at the door.

ZH: 我们需要养成早睡早起的习惯。
EN: We need to develop a habit of going to bed early and getting up early.

ZH: 他不喜欢喝茶,所以他没有喝茶的习惯。
EN: He doesn’t like to drink tea, so he doesn’t have the habit of drinking tea.

ZH: 学会节约用水的习惯对环境保护很重要。
EN: It is important to learn the habit of saving water for environmental protection.

