EN: My grandparents have formed a habit of exercising every day.

ZH: 坚持锻炼是一个好习惯。
EN: Persisting in exercising is a good habit.

ZH: 养成健康的饮食习惯对身体有益。
EN: Developing healthy eating habits is beneficial to the body.

ZH: 年轻的时候养成良好的学习习惯,将获益终生。
EN: Developing good study habits when young will benefit you for a lifetime.

ZH: 不要养成拖延的坏习惯。
EN: Do not develop the bad habit of procrastination.

ZH: 他已经养成了每晚读书的习惯。
EN: He has developed a habit of reading every night.
